7
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:33,680
He must be blaming me.

8
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,360
It's me.

9
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:41,880
I ruined my family.

10
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,360
Ling.

11
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:52,980
[I'll be there for you.] Okay.

12
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:55,890
I'll be with you.

13
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,850
I'll always be with you.

14
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,079
