15
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:34,720
What happened?

16
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:38,880
It has nothing to do with you.

17
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:42,960
You're still blaming me?

18
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:45,560
Blame you?

19
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:46,800
You blame me

20
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:49,130
I killed my mother and brother.

21
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:52,000
I shouldn't have listened to you

22
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:54,360
and insisted on marrying Li Yunxi.

23
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,820
Now that it's come to this,

24
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:56,960
Alright.

25
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,560
I will find the truth

26
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,000
