27
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,360
Why are you laughing?

28
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,660
We've been married for two years.

29
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:28,640
you've never come to me.

30
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:32,640
You have your beloved Snow Consort.

31
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,000
Does it matter

32
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,659
Does it matter?

33
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,370
What were you thinking?

34
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:45,440
Actually, I never told you

35
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:49,200
I really loved you.

36
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:53,260
I thought of you as the person I trusted the most.

37
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,600
Even if I have to give up everything,

38
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:58,520
even if I have to give up everything.

39
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:01,380
What about now?

40
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:04,450
What do you want?

41
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,120
I want you.

42
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,840
Stop talking nonsense.

43
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,760
I finally understand

44
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,960
you gave me the Phoenix Seal.

45
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,400
and married me

46
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:24,320
because you value the military power of the Xiao family

47
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:25,800
