50
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:34,680
You captured my father

51
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:38,490
to deprive the military power of the Xiao family.

52
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,650
Is that what you think of me?

53
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:51,220
This is the lunch box you gave to your father.

54
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,840
He didn't tell you anything,

55
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:54,920
you came to ask me.

56
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,409
I don't understand.

57
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,620
It's clearly because we don't get along.

58
00:06:01,960 --> 00:06:03,490
Why did we make such a scene?

59
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:04,120
Ling,

60
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,840
Why do you think I'll tell you

61
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,280
Do couples

62
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:27,040
quarrel like this?

63
00:06:29,080 --> 00:06:30,210
and fight like this?

64
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:33,170
If you want military power,

65
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:37,659
I will persuade my father to give you the Xiao Troop.

66
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,360
I'll take him back.

67
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,980
and leave the capital.

68
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:46,540
I want to take him away.

69
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:49,240
It's too late.

70
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:51,840
Your Majesty.

71
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,040
It's done.

72
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,460
Send her out of the palace.

73
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:10,920
Get out of the way.

74
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:11,800
His Majesty has ordered that

75
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:14,760
