76
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:16,360
Your Majesty, please leave.

77
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:18,360
You think you can stop me?

78
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:20,970
How dare you stop me?

79
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,850
You're the descendant of the country.

80
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:25,080
How inappropriate!

81
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,250
What about the Empress?

82
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,880
Can't I...

83
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:32,800
Can't I even take a look?

84
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:35,200
No matter what,

85
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:37,200
