89
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:07,960
Her Highness wasn't awake when I went to Palace of Bliss.

90
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:10,090
so I left the letter at Palace of Bliss.

91
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:11,720
That's good.

92
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:14,680
What if

93
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,240
in this letter,

94
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:19,480
Will Her Highness misunderstand you more?

95
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:21,880
Once the assassins are caught,

96
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:26,360
I'll send Ling to see Xiao Rushan.

97
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:39,720
Father.

98
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:41,539
Your Highness.

99
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:44,400
His Majesty has buried General Xiao outside the palace.

100
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:45,330
My condolences.

101
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:47,160
Don't hurt yourself.

102
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:50,900
Your Highness.

103
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:53,960
