109
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:16,680
My mother and brother

110
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:19,080
They met bandits on their way to the border.

111
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:21,370
on the way to the border.

112
00:09:22,160 --> 00:09:23,440
But it's not your fault.

113
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,360
It's my fault.

114
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,720
I missed my mother so much.

115
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:30,530
so I sent her a letter to deliver the sword.

116
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:34,780
Otherwise, she and her brother wouldn't have died.

117
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,960
My father died because of me.

118
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:40,800
Hanxing,

119
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:43,680
You are my only family now.

120
00:09:45,280 --> 00:09:47,040
I will protect you.

121
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:55,600
Father.

122
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:58,800
Ling'er will avenge you.

123
00:10:18,680 --> 00:10:19,540
I didn't expect

124
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,080
