125
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,360
There's white in the dish.

126
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,360
You don't like it?

127
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:36,360
Good wine.

128
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:40,810
If the South Wind knows what I want,

129
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,850
Don't set the sunset

130
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:46,120
At dusk

131
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:48,840
A day like this

132
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:53,320
